        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository ad01b5d6-6f22-4649-b939-76cb439068fd).Image",
        "Description": "One morning, PatrikkiBobi decided to race a jellyfish across Bikini Bottom. With his net in hand, he chased it through the streets, over rocks, and around coral reefs. The jellyfish zipped through the water with ease, while PatrikkiBobi laughed, struggling to keep up. After hours of fun, they reached the finish line together. PatrikkiBobi realized that it wasn’t about winning—it was the thrill of the chase that made the day special.",
